### Dependencies

The workspace utilizes a mix of the Python standard library and third-party dependencies:

```bash
pip install google-genai matplotlib watchdog

```

### Environment Variables

To drive the automated generative flashcard pipeline, you must bind your API token to your system environment profile:

```bash
export GEMINI_API_KEY="your-api-key-here"

```

### Initial Run

Launch the master execution menu to interact with any module across the ecosystem:

```bash
python workspace.py

```
